CSL Mobile Limited Logo CSL Mobile Limited, formerly known as PCCW Mobile HK Limited, is an HKT subsidiary, which operates mobile network brands of “csl”, “1O1O”, “SUN Mobile” and “Club SIM” in Hong Kong. CSL was Hong Kong’s first mobile communications operator established in 1983, and also the first network to launch the world’s first dual band 4G LTE network with DC-HSPA+. Source
